  <brief_title>Intraoperative IV Iron on Postoperative Red Blood Cell Recovery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intraoperative IV Iron on the Postoperative Recovery of Red Blood Cell in Hip Arthroplasty Surgery</official_title>
