  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the present study is to determine the impact of intraoperative IV-iron
      supplementation on postoperative recovery of RBC mass by retrospectively analyzing and
      comparing the changes of postoperative hematocrit values after the surgery in patients
      underwent elective uni-limb total knee arthroplasty surgery with or without IV-iron
      supplementation during surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
